Scenario: Malicious software alters Windows startup folders or registry keys to ensure it boots back up even if the computer restarts.

// Detect modifications to Windows Autorun/Run registry paths for persistence
DeviceRegistryEvents
| where Timestamp > ago(5d)
| where ActionType == "RegistryValueSet"
| where RegistryKey has @"Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run" or RegistryKey has @"Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\RunOnce"
| where RegistryValueData != ""
| project Timestamp, DeviceName, RegistryKey, RegistryValueName, RegistryValueData, InitiatingProcessCommandLine